prodNameC: 威力安 TM II 醣化血紅素分析試劑
ingredientsDesc:
270-0011 Whole Blood Primer. Four vials of lyophilized human red blood cell hemolysate with gentamicin, tobramycin and EDTA as preservatives.
270-2110 Buffer A. Four bottles containing 2000 mL of a Bis-Tris/Phosphate buffer, pH 6.0.
270-2111 Buffer B. One bottle containing 2000 mL of a Bis-Tris/Phosphate buffer, pH 6.0.
270-2112 Wash/Diluent Solution. Two bottles containing 2500 mL of a Bis-Tris buffer, pH 6.6.
270-2113 Analytical Cartridges. Two cation exchange cartridges, 4.6 mm ID x 30 mm.
270-2114 CD-ROM. One CD-ROM with VARIANT II Hemoglobin A1c Program parameters.
270-2115 Calibrator/Diluent Set. One set consisting of three vials of Calibrator Level 1, three vials of Calibrator Level 2 and one bottle of diluent. Lyophilized human red blood cell hemolysate. Diluent contains 120 mL deionized water, pH 7.2.
270-2149 Sample Vials. One hundred sample vials with pierceable caps, 1.5 mL.
applicantName: 美商伯瑞股份有限公司台灣分公司
applicantAddr: 台北市松山區南京東路4段126號14樓
efficacy: VARIANT II醣化血色素檢驗試劑利用離子交換高效能液相層析(HPLC)分離測定血色素A1c。Variant II 醣化血色素檢驗試劑僅適用於Bio-Rad Variant II 血紅素測試系統。僅供體外診斷檢驗試劑。
